"stretch that has been applied as well\n"
"as the amount (thickness of line).\n\n"
"These ajustment annotations are not\n"
"part of the PDF, but are only overlaid\n"
"on the text to help refine the layout.\n\n"
"Key:\n\n"
"Left=shrink       Right=expand\n\n"
"blue=shrink/expand lines\n"
"red=shrink/expand text\n\n"
"Interleaved red+blue indicates\n"
"that both lines and words have\n"
"been stretched/expanded."
